It's not until those lows become unbearable that Mary comes to realize that maybe her Prince Charming isn't such a Prince after all. 5.plot: Young Natalie Purdie has lofty hopes and dreams of becoming a professional dancer in New York after high school in Virginia. Natalie is smitten, but struggles to maintain a clear balance between her goals and the relationship. Their romance blossoms, and she falls in love with the new man in her life. As with many relationships, Melissa soon discovers that romance is not always picture perfect.
